---
---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#0a0b0d]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Visión -->
      <div class="p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all group overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="absolute -right-8 -top-8 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/5 blur-3xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform"></div>
        <div class="mb-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-primary/20 border border-primary/40 animate-pulse"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6">Visión</h3>
        <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed italic">
          "Ser reconocidos como <span class="text-primary font-bold">líder</span> en <span class="text-primary font-bold">comunicaciones y tecnología</span>, sumando socios de negocio en una <span class="text-primary font-bold">plataforma integral</span> que re-defina la forma en la que operan las empresas."
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Misión -->
      <div class="p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all group overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="absolute -right-8 -top-8 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/5 blur-3xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform"></div>
        <div class="mb-6 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-primary/20 border border-primary/40 animate-pulse"></div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6">Misión</h3>
        <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed italic">
          "Integrar <span class="text-primary font-bold">conectividad inteligente</span> con <span class="text-primary font-bold">soluciones</span> tecnológicas que generen valor a nuestros clientes, soportada con un <span class="text-primary font-bold">servicio excepcional</span>."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
